    <h1 class="gd-h1">The Best Time to Go</h1>
    <p class="gd-lede">Iceland gives you one of the longest heliski seasons on earth — March to mid-June — and each month skis like a different sport. This chapter walks the season month by month, weighs powder against corn, and explains the two things that make the far north unforgettable: the Northern Lights and the midnight sun. It is part of our complete <a href="/heliskiing-guide">guide to heliskiing in Iceland</a>.</p>
